	default y
	---help---
	  Say Y here if you want to enable loading OEM kernel splash screen image.
config DISP_EXT_PP
	bool "Enables display color adjustment post processing"
	default y
	---help---
	  Say Y here if you want to enable display color adjustment post processing.
